    "text": [
        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "I'm writing to inform you about a book that influenced me the most.",
        "Firstly,  the book is called \"Maximum Achievement\" by Brian Tracy. This book about self-development teaches you how to manage your time and money effectively. Moreover, the author gives practical advice on ways to implement them in our lives.",
